303
00:31:46,208 --> 00:31:47,876
Selamat, Pak.

304
00:31:48,710 --> 00:31:49,962
Astaga.

305
00:31:51,088 --> 00:31:52,297
Tidak ada hubungan

306
00:31:52,923 --> 00:31:54,800
