saling menanyakan nama.

616
00:54:58,767 --> 00:54:59,935
Kau tahu itu.

617
00:55:00,561 --> 00:55:01,770
Aku Kang Cheong-ya.

618
00:55:02,521 --> 00:55:05,399
Kakekku, seorang aktivis kemerdekaan,
menamaiku begitu

619
00:55:05,482 --> 00:55:07,109
